text: Coral Amiga is an English actress born in London. She is best known for her portrayal of Vorena the Elder, in the television series Rome. After attending The American School in London, she went on to receive a bachelor's degree at New York University. ==Filmography== {| class="wikitable" |- bgcolor="#CCCCCC" ! Year !! Film !! Role !!
